<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Reset Your Password</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; line-height: 1.6;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
        <h2>Reset Your Password</h2>
        <p>Hello,</p>
        <p>We received a request to reset your password. Click the button below to choose a new password. This link is valid for 1 hour.</p>
        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <a href="{{url}}" style="background-color: #007bff; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold;">
                Reset Password
            </a>
        </div>
        <p>If the button doesn't work, you can copy and paste the following link into your browser:</p>
        <p style="word-break: break-all; color: #666; font-size: 14px;">{{url}}</p>
        <p>If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
